# Vallely inventory quality audit.
# Runs daily at 7:20 AM Central, writes a Markdown report, and comments on the configured
# Paperclip issue when stale inventory or missing photos exceed 5%.
#
# Required alert env:
#   PAPERCLIP_API_URL
#   PAPERCLIP_API_KEY
#   VALLELY_INVENTORY_ALERT_ISSUE_ID
#
# Optional:
#   VALLELY_INVENTORY_ALERT_CTO_AGENT_ID
#   PAPERCLIP_RUN_ID
#
20 7 * * * cd /Users/ai_agent_paralles/.paperclip/instances/default/workspaces/5e176133-9730-4a71-af1d-56bcec02147e/paperclip && node scripts/vallely-inventory-audit.mjs --output reports/vallely-inventory-feed-audit.md >> /Users/ai_agent_paralles/.paperclip/instances/default/logs/vallely-inventory-audit.log 2>&1
